README - for wannaporns-65-thai-phrases.pdf

1. Start with the PDF named above.
pdftotext wannaporns-65-thai-phrases.pdf wannaporns-65-thai-phrases.bak

The shell scripts text2html.sh and addsound.sh have the files to operate
on named internally.

./text2html.sh generates wannaporns-65-thai-phrases.html

./addsound.sh operates on a backup copy of the above html file and adds
the sound controls to it.

Read the comments in the shell scripts to understand the use of hexsed
to edit the source files.
